00:38:17.880 --> 00:38:20.750
doors

00:38:33.160 --> 00:38:39.230
will open.

00:38:49.040 --> 00:38:52.309
Father, we open the doors by faith.

00:39:13.750 --> 00:39:13.760
Create

00:39:34.280 --> 00:39:37.510
in

00:40:34.880 --> 00:40:38.190
us a clean heart, oh God.

00:40:42.520 --> 00:40:45.230
We want to be at the spout where the

00:40:45.240 --> 00:40:48.630
glory comes out.

00:40:48.640 --> 00:40:52.390
Come up higher

00:40:52.390 --> 00:40:52.400
in

00:40:52.400 --> 00:40:55.109
your

00:40:55.119 --> 00:40:58.550
prayer life.

00:41:15.040 --> 00:41:20.390
Let the Holy Spirit

00:41:20.400 --> 00:41:23.990
flow

00:41:24.000 --> 00:41:28.589
like a mighty

00:41:28.599 --> 00:41:33.030
river out of our

00:42:19.390 --> 00:42:19.400
bellies.

00:42:34.559 --> 00:42:37.069
Arise and shine, for

00:42:37.079 --> 00:42:39.670
the light has come.

00:42:54.520 --> 00:42:59.030
The joy of the Lord is our

00:42:59.040 --> 00:43:04.270
strength.

00:43:07.640 --> 00:43:10.990
We bind

00:43:11.000 --> 00:43:14.190
depression, anxiety, fear, and

00:43:14.200 --> 00:43:16.990
worry. We

00:43:22.160 --> 00:43:25.589
call

00:46:04.440 --> 00:46:08.950
for a

00:46:08.960 --> 00:46:12.109
harvest of souls like this world has

00:46:12.119 --> 00:46:16.270
never seen.

00:46:31.440 --> 00:46:35.790
We call forth our unsaved

00:46:35.800 --> 00:46:39.349
loved ones to be born again.

00:46:43.069 --> 00:46:43.079
There

00:46:46.440 --> 00:46:49.670
is

00:46:52.910 --> 00:46:52.920
a

00:46:55.480 --> 00:46:58.790
tsunami-sized

00:47:03.640 --> 00:47:06.750
wave of the outpouring

00:47:15.400 --> 00:47:18.430
coming. I've seen

00:47:18.440 --> 00:47:22.710
it. Our prayers are

00:47:22.720 --> 00:47:24.790
drawing the wave in.

00:47:24.800 --> 00:47:28.990
We

00:47:35.549 --> 00:47:35.559
will

00:47:36.800 --> 00:47:39.549
see

00:47:42.910 --> 00:47:42.920
an

00:47:46.559 --> 00:47:50.549
October outpouring

00:47:50.559 --> 00:47:53.069
that

00:47:53.079 --> 00:47:56.150
will hit with such ferocity.

00:48:12.160 --> 00:48:14.910
The church is taking

00:48:18.920 --> 00:48:21.150
on the

00:48:21.160 --> 00:48:24.190
model of Heaven on Earth.

00:48:24.200 --> 00:48:25.870
There

00:48:25.880 --> 00:48:28.030
is

00:48:28.040 --> 00:48:29.670
a wave of

00:48:29.680 --> 00:48:30.960
glory.

00:48:33.480 --> 00:48:41.420
We call forth

00:48:47.430 --> 00:48:47.440
a

00:48:51.200 --> 00:48:55.589
shaking

00:48:58.549 --> 00:48:58.559
of

00:49:01.520 --> 00:49:04.870
your people; we call forth

00:49:04.880 --> 00:49:08.190
awakening.

00:49:25.480 --> 00:49:29.510
Wake up, it's time! Jesus is

00:49:29.520 --> 00:49:32.990
coming. We thank You

00:49:33.000 --> 00:49:36.670
for the fresh

00:49:36.680 --> 00:49:39.309
manifestations

00:49:53.480 --> 00:49:57.190
of the glory.

00:49:57.190 --> 00:49:57.200
It's

00:50:00.309 --> 00:50:00.319
going

00:50:00.319 --> 00:50:05.750
to

00:50:05.760 --> 00:50:09.510
hit

00:50:09.520 --> 00:50:11.910
the

00:50:11.920 --> 00:50:15.750
street corners and the White House.

00:51:08.760 --> 00:51:12.190
We are going to

00:51:12.200 --> 00:51:19.190
overflow.

00:51:48.000 --> 00:51:51.030
Jesus is faithful.

00:51:56.799 --> 00:51:59.630
Put a smile on your face and a song on

00:51:59.640 --> 00:52:04.069
your heart. Jesus loves you.

00:52:06.079 --> 00:52:08.990
Have a wonderful day.

00:52:09.000 --> 00:52:12.960
God bless you. Bye-bye.

